{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/algorithm/4-binarytree-inorder-traversal/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Soobing","author":"[Soobin Bak]","siteUrl":"https://soobing.netlify.com","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"soobing/soobing.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"soobing"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"b812b185-ecac-5fc0-b8d7-41f422485c9b","excerpt":"오늘도 어김없이 의지 활활🔥 Day3가 밝았습니다. 오늘은 binary tree의 traversal관련 문제를 풀어볼껀데요, inorder 방식으로 순회하는 문제를 풀어봅시다!  문제 요약 inorder 방식으로 트리 순회. 단, iteration 방법으로 문제풀기 문제 해결 이 문제는 stack에 현재 순회해야 하는 애들을 쌓아두고  방식으로 순회한다. 1) iteration","html":"<p>오늘도 어김없이 의지 활활🔥 Day3가 밝았습니다. 오늘은 binary tree의 traversal관련 문제를 풀어볼껀데요, inorder 방식으로 순회하는 <a href=\"https://leetcode.com/problems/binary-tree-inorder-traversal/\">문제</a>를 풀어봅시다!</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 1200px;\"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 49.33333333333333%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"binary tree inorder traversal\"\n        title=\"binary tree inorder traversal\"\n        src=\"/static/eeb4908df4fb0940f74cb998b37c2cab/e5166/binarytree-inorder-traversal.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/eeb4908df4fb0940f74cb998b37c2cab/f93b5/binarytree-inorder-traversal.jpg 300w,\n/static/eeb4908df4fb0940f74cb998b37c2cab/b4294/binarytree-inorder-traversal.jpg 600w,\n/static/eeb4908df4fb0940f74cb998b37c2cab/e5166/binarytree-inorder-traversal.jpg 1200w,\n/static/eeb4908df4fb0940f74cb998b37c2cab/d924d/binarytree-inorder-traversal.jpg 1238w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span></p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-요약\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%EC%9A%94%EC%95%BD\" aria-label=\"문제 요약 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 요약</h1>\n<p>inorder 방식으로 트리 순회. 단, iteration 방법으로 문제풀기</p>\n<h1 id=\"문제-해결\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EB%AC%B8%EC%A0%9C-%ED%95%B4%EA%B2%B0\" aria-label=\"문제 해결 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>문제 해결</h1>\n<p>이 문제는 stack에 현재 순회해야 하는 애들을 쌓아두고 <code class=\"language-text\">왼쪽-root-오른쪽</code> 방식으로 순회한다.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-iteration\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#1-iteration\" aria-label=\"1 iteration permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>1) iteration</h2>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"js\"><pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * Definition for a binary tree node.\n * function TreeNode(val) {\n *     this.val = val;\n *     this.left = this.right = null;\n * }\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/**\n * @param {TreeNode} root\n * @return {number[]}\n */</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">var</span> <span class=\"token function-variable function\">inorderTraversal</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">root</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> stack <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> result <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">let</span> node <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> root<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span> <span class=\"token operator\">||</span> stack<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>length <span class=\"token operator\">></span> <span class=\"token number\">0</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">while</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node <span class=\"token operator\">!=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">null</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n            stack<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            node <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>left<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n        node <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> stack<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">pop</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">push</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>val<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        node <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> node<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">return</span> result<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>","frontmatter":{"title":"🎄Binarytree Inorder Traversal","date":"April 04, 2020","thumbnail":{"childImageSharp":{"fixed":{"src":"/static/eeb4908df4fb0940f74cb998b37c2cab/14b42/binarytree-inorder-traversal.jpg"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/algorithm/4-binarytree-inorder-traversal/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/3-symmetric-tree/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🍎 Symmetric Tree","category":"algorithm","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/algorithm/5-maximum-subarray/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"🚇 Maximum Subway","category":"algorithm","draft":false}}}}}